The '''Umboo Racing Team''' was a team for the [[Roon/Legends|Roon]] [[Roon Colonial Games|Colonial Games]] lead by [[Auren Yomm Baobab|Auren Yomm]]. It was consisted of Yomm, her friend [[Gee Long]], and the [[Droid/Legends|droid]] [[BIX]]. They specialized in the [[Drainsweeper/Legends|Drainsweeper]] event. When [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Bisad Koong]] poisoned Long and sabotaged BIX one year during the games, they were replaced by [[Mungo Baobab]] and [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] that year.

